example.de:
[Beispiel 15](https://www.w3.org/TR/activitystreams-vocabulary/#ex12-jsonld)

 ```json 
{
  "@context": "https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams",
  "summary": "Sally created a note",
  "type": "Create",
  "actor": {
    "type": "Person",
    "name": "Sally"
  },
  "object": {
    "type": "Note",
    "name": "A Simple Note",
    "content": "This is a simple note"
  }
}
```

